        "created_at": "2016-01-10T23:40:50.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Interesting note. My sense of the archetypal Lambrays nose is rather different, featuring quite dark fruit tones, smoked duck / grilled game and pungent, spicy earth\u2014but also quite fragrant like the wine you\u2019ve described.</p>\n<p>It sounds like the 2006 is a bit more open for inspection than the 2005 I tasted from 375 last year!</p>",
